Package com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.models

Class Customer

java.lang.Object
com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.models.Customer
public class Customer extends Object
Class for the Customer object. This class is responsible for creating and managing Customer objects. It also contains the birth date and account type information for the customer. This is our basic user class (that will be able to view content). This is called Customer to match the database schema
Author:
Agata (Agy) Olaussen (@agyCoding)
